  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Jenga, a famous license for family and friends, is the unpredictable, quick playing, tactical game that combines suspense and risk-taking, where mounting anticipation comes to a crashing climax. With sophisticated physics, intuitive console controls and a multitude of play options (single and multiplayer) Jenga World Tour contains all the fun of the class IP play with a wealth of possible modifications, power - ups and twists that are only possible in videogame.",
